The '''Rainbow-Eyed Enemy''', or '''Rainbow-Eyed One''', was the name given to [[Shimrra Jamaane]] by the [[Jeedai heresy|''Jeedai'' heretics]] due to his [[mqaaq'it]] implants. It was said among the [[Shamed Ones]] who practiced the heresy that it was his evil that caused the [[Yun'o]] to call down their holy warriors, the ''[[Jeedai]]'', to destroy him.

